引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"b9131a81d3852f1c84905dfa9b27387093a42df1","tid":1981484,"uid":253234,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"Peter你個account有幾多人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD招數一時一樣既"},{"pid":"a90d2a36601e2e43a77a98a15a3aa3fb6a932109","tid":1981484,"uid":95138,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e69afbba54c301dc781b4922b5cd863074433b50","tid":1981484,"uid":49336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"屌曬你班散水撚，同我即刻番poly，poly根本係城堡/要塞黎。邊個話守唔到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"第一，制高點控制，poly控制住所有制高點，要入poly只能經低位行入去，要入就必須頂住高處墮下既磚雨同火魔。<br />\n<br />\n第二，封鎖水炮車，水炮車係poly基本上冇用武之地，佢駛唔入。<br />\n<br />\n第三，一方有難，八方支援。你入cu補給物資要幾耐？入poly要幾耐？物資可謂是無限。<br />\n<br />\n第四，戰略要地，紅隧一塞，會加重埋另兩隧負擔。過海或成不可能任務。<br />\n<br />\n第五，李嘉誠樓位置能360度觀察poly周邊環境。<br />\n<br />\n第六，物資鏈短，舊can去到尖東橋，紅磡橋，新橋，都只係數十米，能極快補給前線。<br />\n<br />\n前題係，人手必須足夠，同埋最好人手一個豬咀！最緊要係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人手呀</span></span>同我即刻過嚟，係咪想成班前線送頭呀！"},{"pid":"f2881ebe131a92ae6ef11e3265f0c1703a8ebde7","tid":1981484,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gi